  m_text: "<b>WELCOME TO THE ASYLUM!</b>\r\n\r\nThe Tidy Ghost is watching your every
    move. <b>Clean the mess</b> before it loses its patience, or you'll be trapped
    here forever!\r\n\r\n<b>NEW TO THE GAME?</b>\r\nIf you need a tutorial, a <b>Training
    Zone</b> is located to your <b>RIGHT</b>. \r\nWalk there using the <b>[W, A,
    S, D]</b> keys.\r\n\r\nOnce you are ready, return here and click <b>START</b>."
